attributes.action: Deport all illegal migrants in the United Kingdom
attributes.additional_details: We think the cost to the taxpayer is crippling and needs to be addressed especially as more than 350,000 people in England are currently homeless. We think the UK is already so over-populated that the current government advocates building on low quality green belt land, or 'grey belt' land.
attributes.background: We think an effective strategy is needed to identify, detain and deport all individuals residing the UK illegally.
